11
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:49,200
And those who trapped me within these pages shall rue locking away this beauty forever.

12
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:53,000
Only your love can set me free.

13
00:01:53,500 --> 00:01:56,200
Go, recite the verse before you quickly...

14
00:01:56,500 --> 00:02:01,000
...lest before me you bend and take a knee.

