32
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:50,000
Ah-ah-ah-ah-ah-ah-ah!

33
00:05:04,828 --> 00:05:10,128
Grow as you may but the necklace will stay just as small as the day it was found.

34
00:05:10,228 --> 00:05:16,128
It's so suffocating, the endless placating, no one is, no one is ever enough.

35
00:05:16,828 --> 00:05:22,128
Won't lose to anyone, always rank number one, aren't you a beautiful child?

36
00:05:22,628 --> 00:05:29,428
Hey! I'm better than her, I'm better than him, oh, everyone come round and gawk at perfection.

37
00:05:29,628 --> 00:05:35,128
Meeting you right after school, I'm finally confessing to you.

38
00:05:35,628 --> 00:05:38,428
Ain't it too good to be true?

39
00:05:38,828 --> 00:05:44,628
A girl like me in love with you, who's miserable, vulgar and crude.

40
00:05:44,828 --> 00:05:49,128
Give me your love, all of your love, give me your love...

41
00:05:49,228 --> 00:05:53,128
...you can have everything if I have you.

42
00:05:53,228 --> 00:05:57,828
I can have you, shoulder my load, now yours to behold.

43
00:05:57,928 --> 00:06:00,628
Still not enough, you're not enough.

44
00:06:00,828 --> 00:06:06,128
Never enough, still I won't lose in my old...

45
00:06:07,128 --> 00:06:10,128
Truly I'm so sorry.

46
00:06:10,228 --> 00:06:14,128
Give me your love, all of your love, give me your love...

47
00:06:14,228 --> 00:06:18,128
...all you can conjure up.

48
00:06:18,228 --> 00:06:22,428
Give me your love, all of your love, till you go mad with ecstasy.

49
00:06:22,528 --> 00:06:25,128
I know it hurts, only gets worse.

50
00:06:25,228 --> 00:06:31,828
God how it hurts, soon you'll be craving the pain.

51
00:06:31,928 --> 00:06:37,128
This is my happiness!

52
00:06:57,228 --> 00:07:03,128
Is this my happiness?

53
00:07:30,428 --> 00:07:32,928
Did you enjoy my lovely song?

54
00:07:33,128 --> 00:07:34,828
I hope you did.

55
00:07:35,028 --> 00:07:37,928
It was for you, after all.

56
00:07:38,828 --> 00:07:42,128
But... why are you not smiling?

57
00:07:42,428 --> 00:07:45,428
Are you not happy to see me?

58
00:07:47,028 --> 00:07:48,628
Well...

59
00:07:48,828 --> 00:07:50,628
Say something. Answer me!

60
00:07:51,128 --> 00:07:53,428
Who... who are you?

61
00:07:53,928 --> 00:07:54,628
What?

62
00:07:54,828 --> 00:07:57,228
You don't know who I am?

63
00:07:57,428 --> 00:08:02,928
But everyone knows. You are the one that released me, right?

64
00:08:03,128 --> 00:08:05,128
I'm... I'm sorry.

65
00:08:05,728 --> 00:08:09,428
You're sorry? For what? For releasing me?

66
00:08:10,428 --> 00:08:11,828
No, no, no.

67
00:08:11,928 --> 00:08:13,628
For upsetting you.

68
00:08:13,828 --> 00:08:16,628
If I said something wrong, I apologize.

69
00:08:16,828 --> 00:08:18,128
Apologize?

70
00:08:18,428 --> 00:08:23,128
You who should be amongst my most dearest and beloved followers...

71
00:08:23,328 --> 00:08:26,128
...who has freed me from that prison...

72
00:08:26,228 --> 00:08:29,128
...who has shown me your love above all others.

73
00:08:29,428 --> 00:08:33,828
You then act like you don't even know who I am?

74
00:08:34,028 --> 00:08:37,128
Why would you toy with my emotions?

75
00:08:37,428 --> 00:08:40,628
I'm sorry, I'm not sure what you mean.

76
00:08:40,828 --> 00:08:42,128
You're not sure what I mean?

77
00:08:42,428 --> 00:08:44,128
Are you mocking me now?

78
00:08:44,628 --> 00:08:47,928
If you truly do not know who I am, then why is it that you set me free?

79
00:08:48,128 --> 00:08:52,128
If not for my love, and if not by your love...

80
00:08:52,228 --> 00:08:54,928
...then for what?

81
00:08:55,128 --> 00:08:58,828
Tell me the truth, and the whole truth, now!

82
00:08:59,428 --> 00:09:02,828
No more lies or there will be consequences.

83
00:09:03,128 --> 00:09:04,828
I... I'm not lying.

84
00:09:05,028 --> 00:09:08,428
I swear to you, I have no idea how I released you.

85
00:09:08,628 --> 00:09:14,128
I just came to a temple to collect rare spices and memories from the many books stowed away here.

86
00:09:14,428 --> 00:09:16,828
By the gods, that's the whole truth.

87
00:09:17,128 --> 00:09:20,928
Extract memories from books?

88
00:09:22,128 --> 00:09:24,928
Are you telling me you're a witch?

89
00:09:25,428 --> 00:09:27,828
How dare you step foot here!

90
00:09:28,128 --> 00:09:33,628
Even knowing the long history between demons and witches, you still dare step foot here?

91
00:09:34,128 --> 00:09:37,128
I know how witches dare to try and bind my kind.

92
00:09:37,928 --> 00:09:41,628
Would you be foolish enough to dare attempt that on me?

93
00:09:42,128 --> 00:09:44,828
Yes, okay. Yes, I'm a witch.

94
00:09:45,028 --> 00:09:48,428
But I've never... well, mostly never, tried anything like that.

95
00:09:48,628 --> 00:09:49,828
I swear.

96
00:09:50,128 --> 00:09:53,128
And this time I was not led on by my nature at all. No.

97
00:09:53,428 --> 00:09:57,928
This time it was an angel that told me of this place.

98
00:09:58,128 --> 00:10:01,628
An angel came to me in my dreams.

99
00:10:04,775 --> 00:10:07,175
An angel came to me in my dreams...

100
00:10:07,175 --> 00:10:09,375
...and told me of an enchanted book
with centuries of memories stored away here.

101
00:10:09,375 --> 00:10:13,275
Can you imagine the knowledge and stories
hidden in centuries of memories?

102
00:10:13,275 --> 00:10:18,775
With a prize like that,
I had to come find the book, no matter the danger.

103
00:10:18,775 --> 00:10:22,175
Little could I have known
the true nature of the book, though...

104
00:10:22,175 --> 00:10:23,275
Enough!

105
00:10:23,275 --> 00:10:25,275
I've heard enough.

106
00:10:25,275 --> 00:10:29,775
I believe you are who you say you are, a witch.

107
00:10:29,775 --> 00:10:33,275
But I don't fully believe your childish story.

108
00:10:33,275 --> 00:10:37,975
No angel would ever lead a witch
to such a dangerous book.

109
00:10:37,975 --> 00:10:42,975
And I can hardly believe it is just the book
and not myself you are after.

110
00:10:42,975 --> 00:10:47,775
It- It's true! An angel came to me
in my dreams and told me to come here.

111
00:10:47,775 --> 00:10:52,075
I was drawn to that book
with all its power and stories.

112
00:10:52,075 --> 00:10:57,775
And, well, I guess you inside it.

113
00:10:57,775 --> 00:11:01,775
The powerful aura it gave off drew me right to it.

114
00:11:01,775 --> 00:11:07,775
How was I to know that the allure was thanks to
a demon trapped within its pages? Who would've guessed?

115
00:11:07,775 --> 00:11:15,775
Though, now that I recount my story,
it does seem it really was me who released you.

116
00:11:15,775 --> 00:11:22,775
Speaking of coming and going, now that you are free,
I think it is time I take my leave of this place.

117
00:11:22,775 --> 00:11:26,675
I'm glad I was able to help free you from...
from whence you came!

118
00:11:26,675 --> 00:11:31,275
I didn't say you could leave!

119
00:11:31,275 --> 00:11:35,775
You may leave when I say you can leave.

120
00:11:35,775 --> 00:11:39,275
And stop your nervous fidgeting.

121
00:11:39,275 --> 00:11:44,775
I'm no fool. You think I didn't see you reaching
for your book of magic?

122
00:11:44,775 --> 00:11:53,275
You, a witch, should know better than anyone
that no amount of magic is powerful enough
to destroy a demon of my power.

123
00:11:53,275 --> 00:12:01,275
However, you can take some small solace
in the fact that if I had wanted you dead,
you'd already be so.

124
00:12:01,275 --> 00:12:06,775
The only reason you're still alive is because
you helped free me.

125
00:12:06,775 --> 00:12:15,275
Alas, I cannot allow a witch who so obviously
came with the intent to bind me to her will
leave here freely.

126
00:12:15,275 --> 00:12:19,275
Your story did little to convince me
your aims were otherwise.

127
00:12:19,275 --> 00:12:22,275
So, I will give you an ultimatum.

128
00:12:22,275 --> 00:12:26,775
You serve me here in my hollow temple.

129
00:12:26,775 --> 00:12:28,775
Love me.

130
00:12:28,775 --> 00:12:30,275
Adore me.

131
00:12:30,275 --> 00:12:32,275
Worship me.

132
00:12:32,275 --> 00:12:36,775
Every living day, give me all the love you have.

133
00:12:36,775 --> 00:12:39,775
Or I can take your soul right now.

134
00:12:39,775 --> 00:12:41,775
Your choice.

135
00:12:41,775 --> 00:12:46,775
Kiara... I need you.

