182
00:16:25,575 --> 00:16:26,175
For what?

183
00:16:26,575 --> 00:16:28,275
For killing a mere witch?

184
00:16:28,675 --> 00:16:30,175
She was not just a witch!

185
00:16:30,675 --> 00:16:32,075
