And a kind-hearted person.

187
00:16:35,575 --> 00:16:37,175
And you killed her

188
00:16:38,075 --> 00:16:39,475
in cold blood.

189
00:16:41,275 --> 00:16:42,975
Oh, the legendary Phoenix,

190
00:16:43,475 --> 00:16:45,975
the mighty fiery Kiara,

191
00:16:46,575 --> 00:16:48,175
friends with a witch?

192
00:16:49,075 --> 00:16:50,675
It's almost funny.

193
00:16:51,375 --> 00:16:52,975
Did you not realize?

194
00:16:53,575 --> 00:16:56,575
It was your witch friend who freed me.

195
00:16:57,075 --> 00:16:57,975
Liar!

196
00:16:58,575 --> 00:17:00,975
She would never do such a ghastly thing.

197
00:17:01,875 --> 00:17:05,975
I trust she would stay away from the dark magics and demonic rituals.

198
00:17:06,475 --> 00:17:10,175
