202
00:17:19,575 --> 00:17:22,175
and unable to see through their deceptions.

203
00:17:22,775 --> 00:17:25,275
Your kind spirit constantly deceives you.

204
00:17:26,175 --> 00:17:28,975
That witch was never your friend.

205
00:17:29,575 --> 00:17:32,075
We all know they cannot be trusted.

206
00:17:32,875 --> 00:17:35,975
Even after all these years, you still have not changed.

207
00:17:37,075 --> 00:17:41,175
Still believing in lies and still so easily misled.

208
00:17:42,475 --> 00:17:44,175
Still such a fool.

209
00:17:45,075 --> 00:17:47,075
It is you who is the fool,

210
00:17:47,475 --> 00:17:48,275
demon!

211
00:17:49,075 --> 00:17:54,075
Your lust for love and attention continues to lead you down the path of death and destruction.

212
00:17:55,175 --> 00:17:58,975
And you don't even see that you're the one destroying your own happiness.

213
00:18:01,075 --> 00:18:03,575
The Gods were right to confine you there.

214
00:18:04,175 --> 00:18:08,075
You, who are still shackled by your lust for love,

215
00:18:08,875 --> 00:18:10,275
your desire for attention,

216
00:18:11,075 --> 00:18:12,875
your desire to be worshipped!

217
00:18:14,075 --> 00:18:16,175
I am the Demon of Sound!

218
00:18:17,275 --> 00:18:20,175
How dare you speak to me in such a manner.

219
00:18:21,175 --> 00:18:24,175
It is but right that all should worship me on their knees.

220
00:18:25,175 --> 00:18:28,175
Their love for none but myself.

221
00:18:29,175 --> 00:18:29,975
Leave!

222
00:18:30,575 --> 00:18:32,175
I have heard enough of your falsities.

223
00:18:33,175 --> 00:18:34,175
This is your last warning.

224
00:18:35,475 --> 00:18:39,075
Go now, or you'll be left to rot here forever!

225
00:18:39,975 --> 00:18:41,575
I am not afraid of you,

226
00:18:42,075 --> 00:18:44,175
and I will heed no such warning.

227
00:18:45,475 --> 00:18:48,275
Listen, and listen well, demon.

228
00:18:49,175 --> 00:18:52,075
I will not allow you to claim any more victims.

229
00:18:53,075 --> 00:18:56,975
To be banished in a void was not sufficient enough punishment for you.

230
00:18:59,475 --> 00:18:59,975
No.

231
00:19:00,575 --> 00:19:04,175
